headline: Teradyne Declares Quarterly Cash Dividend and Increases Share Repurchase Plan for 2024
summary: NORTH READING, Mass., November 11, 2024--Teradyne, Inc. (NASDAQ:TER) today announced a quarterly cash dividend of $0.12 per share, payable on December 18, 2024, to shareholders of record as of the close of business on November 25, 2024.
